author: wcax.com
title: New Hampshire police investigate one-car fatal
text:
WOLFEBORO, N.H. (AP) - New Hampshire police are investigating a fatal, one-car crash in Wolfeboro.
WMUR-TV reports ( http://bit.ly/1OuG55P ) that police believe speed may have been a factor in the crash on Beach Pond Road Saturday night.
Authorities have not released the name of the driver, pending notification of family members.
Multiple agencies responded to the crash, which happened at 10:15 p.m. Saturday.
